 Monday Mar 18 Finish Letter 13 to B.E. Tue . 19 Wed . 20 Thur . 21 Big dinner without the Band again . Got letter from Geo Herford . Wrote Another . Fritz attack on a 60 mile front , from the River Oise , near La Fere , to the Seux River , south east of Arras , forc a withdraw of posit of the British Line . Friday 22nd Mar Fritz commenc his Big offens yesterday . Not much news in the paper accord to report he has 95 divis on the West Front face the British , so we must expect thing to happen . German claim 16,000 prison and 200 Gun . Sat . 23 Fritz claim a big number of prison and Gun but our Line is unbroken . " Yank " finish up and a new chap took over his Job .
